Type Property# withoutChanges

iOS 2.0+iPadOS 2.0+Mac Catalyst 13.0+macOS 10.0+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
static var withoutChanges: NSFileCoordinator.ReadingOptions { get }
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Foundation/NSFileCoordinator/ReadingOptions/withoutChanges#Discussion)

Specify this constant if your code does not need other objects to save changes first. If you do *not* specify this constant, the [`savePresentedItemChanges(completionHandler:)`](/documentation/foundation/nsfilepresenter/savepresenteditemchanges(completionhandler:)) method of relevant file presenters is called before your code reads the item.
